des: Play an INSANE and BEAUTIFUL game of quiz with Alexa. ONLY the the smartest will make it through... CAN YOU? While playing the quiz, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next question. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the quiz.
